Slackware Current Repository by Conraid

======================================================================

wine-mono (Wine's built-in replacement for MS .NET Framework)

Wine Mono is a package containing Framework Mono and other projects,
intended as a replacement for the .NET Framework (4.8.1 and earlier)
in Wine. It works in conjunction with Wine's builtin mscoree.dll,
and it is not intended to be useful for any other purpose.

HOME: https://www.winehq.org/

